2019-04-10

Updated database routines to work with PHP7 and Mysqli
Updated authentication to hashed and salted passwords. 
	This required a change to the user table. 
	Changed from cookie sessions to PHP sessions.
Added ability to remember a logon as option. 
	This required a change to the user table.
Changed structure so all pages are accessed through the index.php file.
Fixed a sorting bug.
Added ability to change the display of dates.
Added ability to have all entries show just the heading by default.
Updated the display format.
Added a timer to refresh the side pane every 10 minutes. Adjustable from the config file.
Fixed the sort button in the top menu.
Multiple other code clean ups and optimizations.
